  hindiTitle `हरियाणा और पंजाब कृषि विश्‍वविद्यालय अधिनियम, 1970`
  actYear (1970)
  ministry `Ministry of Agriculture and Farmers Welfare`
  department `Department of Agricultural Research and Education`
